Task 7: Triggers, Views, and Exceptions 

Objective:

To understand and implement Triggers, Views, and Exception Handling for performing and 

managing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations in an Oracle database.

Part 1: Implementing Triggers

1. Prevent Insertion of Underage Students

2. Create a Log Table
